text: "This Is Where I Came In" is a 2001 song by Bee Gees and is the title track to their 22nd and final studio album This Is Where I Came In. It went to number 18 in the United Kingdom, number 24 in Scotland, number 76 in Australia, number 42 in Austria, number 41 in Switzerland, number 25 in Germany and number 37 in New Zealand. ==Track listings== ==References== Category:2001 songs Category:Bee Gees songs
